        </div>
      </li>
      <li class={cn(item)}>
        <img
          class={cn(icon)}
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          src="https://csimg.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/Images/Icons/red-hourglass.svg"
          alt="icon"
          width="32"
          height="32"
        />
        <div class={cn(itemWrapper)}>
          <h3 class={cn(h3)}>Programs for Proper Weight Loss</h3>
          <p class={cn(itemText)}>
            Take advantage of our spacious gym equipped with a wide range of gym
            fitness machines so you can achieve.
